        },
        {
            "title": "瑞銀認為宏觀背景利好將持續推動全球股市上漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8keWc9V9Qk2Xi3e6pVT.cg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEEA70L9_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 全球股市已反彈至歷史新高,瑞銀認為這波漲勢將持續下去,預計穩健的基本面、關稅阻力緩解以及結構性增長趨勢的組合將推動廣泛的盈利增長,一直持續到2026年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">策略師Fabian Deriaz表示:\"整體宏觀背景依然具建設性,受到關稅阻力緩解、聯準會預期降息、支持性財政政策以及製造業復甦的支撐。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀對全球股市維持\"吸引力\"評級,並預計今年MSCI全球指數的每股盈利將增長12%,稱這一增幅\"相當可觀,並提供了緩衝空間\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d2a57289-877b-361d-a97d-dcaa610d4d45-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構承認,鑑於石油供應仍受到嚴重干擾,市場正在為樂觀結果定價,但認為當前格局仍有利於進一步上漲。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀補充說,投資者倉位未能跟上價格步伐,許多投資者在局勢升級階段降低了風險敞口,錯過了反彈,Deriaz將這種動態比作去年4月關稅驅動的拋售,當時重建倉位幫助推動市場創下新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在板塊和地區偏好方面,瑞銀因其週期性和結構性吸引力而看好全球工業板塊,並建議在美國採取槓鈴策略,重點關注非必需消費品、金融、醫療保健和公用事業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首選市場包括美國、日本、新興市場和瑞士。在人工智能領域,瑞銀採取更具選擇性的方法,專注於\"美國大型科技股以外的機會——尤其是中國科技公司\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">需要監控的關鍵風險包括荷莫茲海峽重新開放的時機以及科技板塊內日益激烈的競爭。瑞銀還指出,動能策略的過度擁擠可能成為波動性的潛在來源。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%80%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%A5%BD%E5%B0%87%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-123021167.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 20:40:34",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "AMD與Arm股價上漲:CPU與GPU比例變化如何重塑AI市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C7XPfeVSxETz0.J6_5.vow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5I05A_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週五,超微半導體(NASDAQ:AMD)股價上漲12%,而Arm Holdings(NASDAQ:ARM)上漲8%,此前市場對人工智慧CPU熱潮已經到來的預期不斷升溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">CPU(中央處理器)是電腦和伺服器中的主要處理器,負責處理一般運算任務。這與GPU(圖形處理器)形成對比,GPU專門用於並行處理,一直是AI訓練中使用的主要晶片。AMD為資料中心和個人電腦製造CPU和GPU,而Arm則設計CPU架構並授權給晶片製造商。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2f63878e-294f-30d4-a02a-eee96dde1895-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這波漲勢是在英特爾公布強勁季度業績並上漲27%之後出現的,其推動力來自強勁的伺服器CPU需求。這一勢頭反映了AI基礎設施需求的轉變,因為較新的AI工作負載相對於GPU需要更多的CPU容量。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Northland分析師Gus Richard的說法,AI系統中的CPU與GPU比例在不同應用中正在發生劇烈變化。該比例從訓練的1:8轉變為推理的1:4,再到代理AI的1:2,顯示伺服器CPU需求正在加速增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Evercore ISI分析師Mark Lipacis指出,成長最快的AI工作負載需要更多的CPU,甚至可能將CPU:GPU比例從1:8翻轉至8:1,他稱之為「CPU復興」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">RBC Capital分析師Srini Pajjuri評論稱,「在代理AI的推動下,伺服器CPU需求持續超過供應」,並暗示儘管該板塊競爭激烈,但這一趨勢可能會持續到2027年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Stifel分析師Ruben Roy觀察到,在伺服器市場的所有業務領域,需求持續大幅超過供應,銷量和價格都對這一強勁表現做出了貢獻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/amd%E8%88%87arm%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-cpu%E8%88%87gpu%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E8%AE%8A%E5%8C%96%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%87%8D%E5%A1%91ai%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-123006001.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 20:40:36",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
